Package: lydemapr
Type: Package
Title: Mapping the Spread of Lycorma delicatula
Version: 3.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Seba", "De Bona", email = "sebastiano.debona@temple.edu", role = c("cre", "aut")),
    person("Matt", "Helmus", email = "mrhelmus@temple.edu", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Seba De Bona <sebastiano.debona@temple.edu>
URL: https://github.com/ieco-lab/lydemapr,
    https://ieco-lab.github.io/lydemapr/
BugReports: https://github.com/ieco-lab/lydemapr/issues
Description: This package contains aggregated, anonymized data on the presence/absence and population density of the Spotted Lanternfly (Lycorma delicatula) in the United States. The package contains functions to display the data through both table summaries and maps.
